VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT EditText\.getText\(\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(execute|query|rawQuery|execSQL|Runtime|ProcessBuilder|File\s*\(|URL\s*\(|WebView|loadUrl|loadData) && MISSING:(validate|sanitize|escape|encode|allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of user input fields, such as EditTexts, which may contain untrusted inputs.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: User Input Fields.
